reviewText: I bought this, because I thought my grandson, who at the time seemed taken with birds would enjoy it. However, I found it so relaxing for myself that I'm keeping it! Of course he can always watch along.

Winged Wonders is a pleasant DVD to watch.  If you are already a bird watcher and delight at seeing your favorites, or are a novice hoping to learn the names of the various birds that visit your yard, this DVD is delightful to watch.
